":"","text":"值得收藏的文艺语句​ “可是这假意浪漫的万物中，只有你才是我所要描摹的真身。” “城市的夜空只有月亮。想你的时候，把湖面的镜子敲碎，让星星一颗、一颗浮上来。” “没有你，我的时间是缓慢的米勒行星”","categories":[{"name":"Article","slug":"Article","permalink":"http://weiweii.top/categories/Article/"}],"tags":[],"author":"ww"}],"categories":[{"name":"Tool","slug":"Tool","permalink":"http://weiweii.top/categories/Tool/"},{"name":"Article","slug":"Article","permalink":"http://weiweii.top/categories/Article/"}],"tags":[]}